snippet.title: Dragon of Legends - Kickstarter Video
snippet.description:
Dragon of Legends is now LIVE on Kickstarter! Head on over to the campaign page here: http://kck.st/1omOwaE

Reward tiers start from as little as $10 and we would be eternally grateful if you backed it, but even if you can't - please consider sharing this video among your personal networks, or with anyone you think that would enjoy our game.

www.dragonoflegends.com
